== 評價==
《[[芝加哥太陽報|芝加哥太陽報]]》影評{{link-en|理查·洛普|Richard Roeper}}在滿分四顆星之中給了三顆星，表示這部作品「是一部厚臉皮且寓教於樂的髒話題材作品。」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2021/1/4/22211549/history-swear-words-review-netflix-nicolas-cage-documentary|title='History of Swear Words': Netflix doc filthy rich with insight about obscenities|website=[[Chicago_Sun-Times|Chicago Sun-Times]]|first=Richard|last=Reoper|date=January 4, 2021|access-date=January 8, 2021|archive-date=2021-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110023937/https://chicago.suntimes.com/movies-and-tv/2021/1/4/22211549/history-swear-words-review-netflix-nicolas-cage-documentary|dead-url=no}}</ref>

據[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上的18則評論，這部作品獲得67%的好評，平均分數為6.13/10，評論家認為「言簡意賅或許是智慧的精髓，但深入地研究有助理解髒話的歷史，這部作品的內容沒有辜負它的標題和主持人，可惜他X的有點短」<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/history_of_swear_words/s01|title=History of Swear Words: Season 1 (2021)|work=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|access-date=January 14, 2021|archive-date=2021-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301201105/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/tv/history_of_swear_words/s01|dead-url=no}}{{cbignore}}</ref>。而據[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上的13則評論，此作品獲得的加權均分是62分（滿分為100分），評價以正面為多。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.metacritic.com/tv/history-of-swear-words/season-1|title=History of Swear Words: Season 1|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|access-date=January 7, 2021|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126024153/https://www.metacritic.com/tv/history-of-swear-words/season-1|dead-url=no}}{{cbignore}}</ref>

